sg":"係唔係文藝片黎<br />\n今集d背景音樂又咩事"},{"pid":"dd1d9d95c9117664e29cd326936d6381c2691a28","tid":345371,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔係文藝片黎<br />\n今集d背景音樂又咩事</blockquote><br />\n前段關懷導盲犬，後段借劇中嘅「廣告」片段，變咗男女主角關懷之情。<br />\n順帶一提，女主角胡杏兒，為勞福局拍「尊重工作中導盲犬」宣傳廣告，<br />\n應該係源自呢套劇。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07b35cb230ebb2885bb359c2e59aa94dcbf4e4b","tid":345371,"uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"呢套真係好好睇 成套劇好有正能量<br />\n人際關係同都市生活兩個主題環環相扣得好好 好自然，生活化 <br />\n人物塑造得好立體<br />\n<br />\n我覺得陪著你走係套有靈魂既好劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d923ba3adc560c9af7d8989682389734e309ca8","tid":345371,"uid":90038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:36:20.000Z","msg":"幾like胡杏兒首主題曲"},{"pid":"b3a6dee4d07e8c8116b1e8b6532ab0b3180fcd2f","tid":345371,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾like胡杏兒首主題曲</blockquote><br />\n我都覺"},{"pid":"a6862baaee94ed52021985c53669dbd63f9beae3","tid":345371,"uid":59925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"真係好高質，我諗往後都好難再有類似的劇集，每個角色都好好，首主題曲都聽左2年幾，好多位都唔會用對白刻意講出黎，等觀眾自己感受"},{"pid":"c66ec6239abf6c95c7817c9b3be8e6e37050b2d8","tid":345371,"uid":90038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T19:59:42.000Z","msg":"金荷娜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beea61fcd2002b105e36f105773233c5d35bc9d2","tid":345371,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"大結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de40dbad1c9f6721ad1a2c07caceeba96fd0988f","tid":345371,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit